msgid "U\\left|\\psi\\right\\rangle = \\begin{pmatrix} r_0e^{it_0}\\\\ r_1e^{it_1}\\\\ . \\\\ . \\\\ r_{2^{n-1}-1}e^{it_{2^{n-1}-1}} \\end{pmatrix}\\otimes\\left|0\\right\\rangle\n\n"
